This is just the main part, which is played during the first few minutes of the song.
This doesn't include the beginning part, in which Hendrix is just soloing and stuff like that.
This is just the basic outline, and he adds stuff in there, which is what made him such 
great guitarist.
Just add your own little stuff into this when playing.
(I would play it legatto, or smoothly)

